				<h1 itemprop="headline" class="entry-title">Today in Small Business: From the Web to Bricks and Mortar</h1>
		<div class="story-meta-footer">
			<address class="byline author vcard" itemprop="author creator" itemtype="//schema.org/Person">
				By Gene Marks			</address>
			<!-- date published --><time class="dateline " datetime="2014-03-24T17:08:57+00:00" itemprop="datePublished">March 24, 2014 1:08 pm</time>
			<!-- date updated --><span class="visually-hidden updated">March 24, 2014 1:08 pm</span><button class="button comments-button  theme-kicker" data-skip-to-para-id="">
