		<div class="entry-content"><p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><div id="sharetools-story" class="sharetools theme-classic sharetools-story" data-shares="email|Email,facebook|Share,twitter|Tweet,save|Save,show-all|More,ad" data-url="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/03/24/today-in-small-business-from-the-web-to-bricks-and-mortar/" data-title="Today in Small Business: From the Web to Bricks and Mortar" data-description="Getting people to read your emails. How G.M. is using social media to manage its reputation. Are you really as busy as you say you are?">
				<div class="ad sharetools-inline-article-ad"></div>
				<div id="MiddleLeft" class="ad middle-left-ad nocontent robots-nocontent"></div>
				</div><div class="inlineModule"><div class="entry"><h6 class="kicker"><a href="//boss.blogs.nytimes.com/category/dashboard/">Dashboard</a></h6><p class="summary">A daily roundup of small-business developments.</p></div></div></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">Whatâs affecting me, my clients and other small-business owners today.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>The Economy</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Many business economists <a href="//www.reuters.com/article/2014/03/24/us-usa-economy-rates-idUSBREA2N06320140324?f">see an interest rate</a> hike coming.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Gas prices <a href="//time.com/35061/us-gas-prices-up-4-dollars-per-tank/">have gone up</a> $4 a tank over the last six weeks.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ In March, growth in <a href="//www.reuters.com/article/2014/03/24/us-usa-economy-markit-idUSBREA2N0S420140324">factory activity</a> slowed slightly.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Eswar S. Prasad explains why the <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/03/22/opinion/why-the-dollar-endures.html">dollar endures</a>: &#8220;The supply of safe assets has shrunk. Bonds issued by most euro-zone countries look shaky in the aftermath of the euro-zone debt crisis, especially since many of these countries face weak growth prospects. Countries like Japan and Switzerland have taken steps to weaken their currencies (thereby shoring up their exports) and are intervening in foreign exchange markets to prevent their currencies from appreciating in value. Thus they are adding to the demand for safe assets.&#8221; <span id="more-83817"></span></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Sales and Marketing</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Another Web retailer, Birchbox, decides to <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/03/24/business/birchbox-seller-of-beauty-products-steps-out-from-web-with-a-store.html">open a bricks-and-mortar store</a>.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ How a small maker of snacks became <a href="//www.washingtonpost.com/business/route-11-potato-chips-finds-success-as-a-cult-favorite-in-a-fiercely-competitive-market/2014/03/21/56551306-aa10-11e3-b61e-8051b8b52d06_story.html">a cult favorite</a>.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Developers are using <a href="//online.wsj.com/news/articles/SB10001424052702304185104579437590964522278">custom scents</a> to get buyers to warm up to a home.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here are four steps to get <a href="//www.roundpeg.biz/2014/03/write-professional-emails/">people to read</a> your emails.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ <a href="//www.buffalonews.com/business/small-companies-pound-pavement-to-get-deals-20140323">Thereâs no magic</a> that gets a small business a deal with big companies â it takes good old-fashioned pavement pounding.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><strong>Social Media</strong></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ How General Motors is using social media to try <a href="//www.nytimes.com/2014/03/24/business/after-huge-recall-gm-speaks-to-customers-through-social-media.html">to manage its online reputation</a>.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Jimmy Kimmel and the Clintons <a href="//www.nydailynews.com/news/politics/jimmy-kimmel-tweets-hilarious-selfie-clinton-family-article-1.1731113">do a</a> selfie.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Productivity</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A <a href="//www.slate.com/articles/double_x/doublex/2014/03/brigid_schulte_s_overwhelmed_and_our_epidemic_of_busyness.html">new book</a> says youâre not as busy as you say you are.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Ideas</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Delta <a href="//www.avionics-intelligence.com/articles/2014/03/delta-innovation.html">introduces</a> âInnovation Class,&#8221; which connects the airline&#8217;s LinkedIn community with industry leaders at 35,000 feet.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ A new wearable tech product <a href="//thenextweb.com/gadgets/2014/03/24/wearable-tech-tracking-cows-heat-sure/?u">tracks</a> when cows are in heat.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Health Care</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Robert Reich says, âObamacare <a href="//www.nytimes.com/roomfordebate/2014/03/20/obamacares-four-year-checkup/the-affordable-care-act-is-working-despite-misinformation">is working</a>.â</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ The health insurance law is <a href="//upstart.bizjournals.com/companies/innovation/2014/03/22/obamacare-coriell-life-science.html?">providing a business opportunity</a> for this personalized medicine start-up.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Entrepreneurship</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ In August, a father and his eighth-grade son started a toy company selling kits to create hours of fantasy fun with cardboard boxes, and they <a href="//www.heraldextra.com/news/local/teenaged-highland-business-owner-just-plane-successful/article_de5e4c5f-ac34-5836-8d9f-fef840935d42.html">have now expanded</a> to nearly all 50 states and three countries.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody"><b>Bitcoin</b></p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Mt. Gox <a href="//pando.com/2014/03/21/mtgox-finds-200000-bitcoin-down-the-back-of-the-couch/">finds 200,000 Bitcoins</a> âdown the back of the couch.â</p>
