<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Accountants say that <a href="//www.marketwired.com/press-release/xero-survey-reveals-biggest-tax-time-mistakes-offers-financial-advice-small-businesses-1889715.htm">the biggest mistake</a> small businesses can make is talking to them only at tax time.</p>
<p class="story-body-text" itemprop="articleBody">â¢ Here are a few strategies for <a href="//blog.shoeboxed.com/if-you-cant-pay-your-taxes/9649/">when you canât pay</a> your taxes.</p>
